        <tag>hexo</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>hwxo分类和标签设置</title>
    <url>/hwxo%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E5%92%8C%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><p>新建page页面</p>
<p>分类</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>标签</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n page tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在source目录找到对应的categories和tags目录，在目录中找到index.md，编辑index.md的Front-matter部分。如下；</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: Hello World</span><br><span class="line">date: 2023-04-06 15:28:11</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在data：下面添加</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">type: categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在data：下面添加</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">type: tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在data：下面添加</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tags: hexo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

]]></content>
